column4: The Ninjala Tournament held in collaboration with{=br}Jujutsu Kaisen will be open simultaneously worldwide!{=br}There's an exclusive Sticker available just for participating,{=br}plus exclusive emotes and tons of other awesome rewards for top ranking players!{=br}Be sure to join in and aim for the top in the Ninjala Tournament!{=br}{=br}*Tournament rankings are calculated separately from normal rankings. {=br}*Tournament rewards will be sent to your in-game mailbox after the tournament rankings have been finalized.
